                        <interp inst="t18391021-2730-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 26.—
<rs id="t18391021-2730-punishment-33" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18391021-2730-punishment-33" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-2730-18391021 t18391021-2730-punishment-33"></join>Transported for Seven Years</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Justice Bosanquet</hi>..</p>
